{"tid":920870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★人體實驗！每日進食該國漢堡、炸雞、燒烤，3年後支人血液變成粉紅色","createTime":"2018-11-29T06:56:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T08:34:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":55,"dislike":56,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"40d03eec0a96d56967c55647420d254c2258ed4e","tid":920870,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:56:54.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢一名十七歲錢姓女生近日突然腹痛難耐入院，經檢查後發現全身血液竟變成粉紅色，連儀器亦無法識別。原來事主三年來幾乎每日進食漢堡、炸雞、燒烤等「垃圾食物」，並只喝可樂不飲清水，加上本身患有家族傾向性糖尿病而不自知，導致最後險進鬼門關。幸而經醫護人員緊急搶救，並連續三天為其血液清理出八公升白色「脂肪液」，錢女已脫離危險期，目前正留院觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20181129/photo/1129-00178-023b2.jpg?t=1543474591337\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20181129%2Fphoto%2F1129-00178-023b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1543474591337&h=66b01699&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20181129/00178_023.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20181129%2F00178_023.html&d=25Bn80kblrlf5eFaRga00gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=580c8de7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20181129/00178_023.html</a>"},{"pid":"e46a47eef21deb98e0709fb696267a650777bf94","tid":920870,"uid":19454,"like":467,"dislike":4,"score":463,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HxLwbHt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHxLwbHt.jpg&h=bd9ba5cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3940a30760fcd848861017f13c0294e95797a5c","tid":920870,"uid":26752,"like":154,"dislike":2,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T06:59:13.000Z","msg":"支荒血<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e2d6b6de09e907531acd1fce729d050393b0c2","tid":920870,"uid":102096,"like":170,"dislike":8,"score":162,"citedBy":5,"repl